    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I'm selling my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. You\u2019ll find it\u2019s clean, well-loved, and totally ready for its next adventure with you! It\u2019s the perfect balance of quality and value. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a great new home!",
