    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a hallmark of analog performance. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a VANOS overhaul, ensuring the chassis handles the torsional loads expected of an M-car. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings and dampers. This is a driver's car engineered for technical precision and high-lateral-G stability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_3",
