      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This well-maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and value. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though closer inspection reveals minor stone chips and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful road use. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin with premium upholstery that remains supportive and comfortable, showing only light wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every button, switch, and climate control setting functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is solid; it has been serviced at regular intervals, providing a smooth ride with crisp gear shifts and responsive handling. It comes equipped with a power sunroof, an upgraded sound system, and a suite of safety features that make it an ideal daily driver. If you are looking for a reliable, attractive car that has been treated with respect, this is an excellent choice.",
