      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a purist's specification featuring the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six and a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This vehicle excels in performance, with the high-revving power plant delivering a crisp 8,000 RPM redline through its individual throttle bodies. Essential enthusiast maintenance has been proactively completed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and structural subframe reinforcement to mitigate common chassis fatigue. The M Variable Differential Lock remains tight, ensuring optimal power distribution across the rear axle. While the finish shows light road wear, the suspension geometry remains true, and the hydraulic steering rack offers the tactile feedback these cars are famous for. This is a robust, high-performance example ready for the apex.",
